author: Marisa Schultz
title: Protesters gather at Minnesota governor's mansion over lockdown, chant 'open up'
description: Protesters gathered outside of the Minnesota governor's mansion Friday rebelling against coronavirus stay-at-home orders and demanding an end the lockdown, chanting "open up."
